All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable
public class HTMLComponent
extends Component

Component subtype representing arbitrary HTML. Questions used to be a mix of HTMLComponents and StringComponents when the RESOURCE column was in use. Now a question is one of an HTMLComponent or StringComponent.
